00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:33.340
How much longer

00:03:33.659 --> 00:03:34.379
can you endure?

00:03:35.099 --> 00:03:37.020
Not only are you broke,

00:03:37.419 --> 00:03:38.900
but you're begging here.

00:03:39.539 --> 00:03:41.340
