00:04:20.420 --> 00:04:21.459
Surprised, right?

00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:25.139
Two years ago?

00:04:26.620 --> 00:04:29.060
Why could he

00:04:29.740 --> 00:04:30.699
know Grand Tutor Zhou?

00:04:31.339 --> 00:04:32.180
Impossible.

00:04:33.219 --> 00:04:34.459
He's never told me.

00:04:35.819 --> 00:04:36.500
Two years ago

00:04:37.180 --> 00:04:39.180
was when I first met Youshou.

00:04:40.139 --> 00:04:41.379
Could he have already...

00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:43.259
Let me finish.

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:46.699
Two years ago,

00:04:47.540 --> 00:04:49.379
Grand Tutor Zhou discovered

00:04:49.620 --> 00:04:52.300
suspicious expenses
of 500 liang in the Xue Mansion.

00:04:53.860 --> 00:04:54.420
So,

00:04:54.660 --> 00:04:56.060
