00:04:56.779 --> 00:04:57.980
I tracked down

00:04:58.779 --> 00:05:00.259
and found Xue Youshou.

00:05:01.699 --> 00:05:02.540
He was

00:05:02.540 --> 00:05:03.540
putting on

00:05:03.899 --> 00:05:04.980
mystical airs.

00:05:05.899 --> 00:05:07.620
No matter what,

00:05:08.139 --> 00:05:09.180
I brought him back

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:10.459
for the Grand Tutor.

00:05:14.219 --> 00:05:14.940
Soon after,

00:05:15.459 --> 00:05:16.139
