00:05:17.379 --> 00:05:18.740
appeared in the palace.

00:05:21.139 --> 00:05:22.740
It's Xue Youshou himself.

00:05:25.300 --> 00:05:27.259
Before Grand Tutor Zhou
tried to kill you,

00:05:27.980 --> 00:05:29.459
did he act strangely?

00:05:33.300 --> 00:05:33.819
First,

00:05:34.660 --> 00:05:35.980
he sent people after you.

00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:37.339
Second,

00:05:38.339 --> 00:05:39.300
recently,

00:05:39.819 --> 00:05:41.019
when Feng Zuoren went south

00:05:41.219 --> 00:05:42.660
to find the former Crown Prince,

00:05:42.940 --> 00:05:44.740
Grand Tutor Zhou sent me too.

00:05:46.300 --> 00:05:47.019
I discovered

00:05:47.860 --> 00:05:49.620
it was Xue Youshou again.

00:06:01.219 --> 00:06:03.180
So I brought him back
to the Grand Tutor.

00:06:04.180 --> 00:06:05.139
Guess what?

00:06:06.379 --> 00:06:07.139
Grand Tutor Zhou

00:06:08.300 --> 00:06:09.379
kept it secret.

00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:13.980
Third,

00:06:15.459 --> 00:06:16.219
I saw

00:06:17.219 --> 00:06:19.860
Xue Youshou visiting
the Grand Tutor Zhou,

00:06:21.540 --> 00:06:22.540
saying something like,

00:06:23.860 --> 00:06:24.860
"Proceed with the plan."

00:06:40.699 --> 00:06:41.980
Proceed with the plan.

00:06:45.540 --> 00:06:46.259
Then,

00:06:48.259 --> 00:06:49.300
I got hunted down.

00:06:51.379 --> 00:06:54.019
Grand Tutor Zhou is colluding

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:56.540
with Young Master?

00:06:58.660 --> 00:07:00.579
Are you just making up a story

00:07:00.740 --> 00:07:01.819
as you hate Grand Tutor?

00:07:04.060 --> 00:07:05.379
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:07:09.459 --> 00:07:11.819
(Xue Youshou falsely claimed
to be Young Master,)

00:07:12.699 --> 00:07:14.779
(now he's colluding
with Grand Tutor Zhou.)

00:07:15.379 --> 00:07:16.579
