00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.459
You're still defending her
at this point?

00:07:39.899 --> 00:07:41.180
Have you fallen for her?

00:07:41.459 --> 00:07:42.100
I'm not blind.

00:07:43.019 --> 00:07:43.620
Rest assured.

00:07:44.579 --> 00:07:45.860
