00:08:01.180 --> 00:08:01.860
Your Majesty.

00:08:02.219 --> 00:08:04.860
This is red date congee
prepared by the imperial chefs.

00:08:05.100 --> 00:08:07.339
With astragalus, angelica,

00:08:07.459 --> 00:08:08.860
longan, and red dates.

00:08:09.139 --> 00:08:11.100
Formulated to regulate your digestion

00:08:11.379 --> 00:08:12.699
