00:13:24.579 --> 00:13:25.459
You!

00:13:25.859 --> 00:13:26.940
Xue Hexu, you go first!

00:13:27.060 --> 00:13:27.619
Don't mind me.

00:13:34.339 --> 00:13:34.940
