00:16:15.739 --> 00:16:16.300
All I can do

00:16:17.540 --> 00:16:19.699
is to paint you blossoms...

00:16:21.300 --> 00:16:22.739
Brew cherry blossom wine,

00:16:23.260 --> 00:16:23.819
and

00:16:25.060 --> 00:16:26.979
make cherry blossom cakes.

00:16:27.819 --> 00:16:28.979
I'll paint pink petals

00:16:29.540 --> 00:16:30.140
on...

00:16:31.260 --> 00:16:32.699
on the kite for you.

00:16:35.940 --> 00:16:37.339
When it soars high...

00:16:38.459 --> 00:16:39.739
- It's like cherry blossoms dancing.
- It's like cherry blossoms dancing.

